    "rule":  "du (informell) für Freunde/Familie, Sie (formell) für Unbekannte/Chefs.",
    "explanation":  "German has two ways to say \u0027you\u0027. \u0027du\u0027 is informal (close relationships), \u0027Sie\u0027 is formal (professional/strangers). Choosing the right one is essential for social politeness.",
