                                        "type":  "concept",
                                        "title":  "Grundkonzept · Basic Concept",
                                        "text":  "How you address someone in German depends on your relationship. \u0027du\u0027 is for friends and family, while \u0027Sie\u0027 is used for strangers and formal social settings.",
