                                                        "du → children, family, close friends, pets",
                                                        "Sie → adults you don\u0027t know, superiors, officials",
                                                        "The plural of \u0027du\u0027 is \u0027ihr\u0027 (multi-person informal)",
                                                        "The plural of \u0027Sie\u0027 is \u0027Sie\u0027 (capitalized!)"
